Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.00,0:00:07.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Can't you see that you are sweet？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.50,0:00:16.20,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Oh Let me love you so
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.50,0:00:30.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}見上げる空は遠いけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.50,0:00:37.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}抱えきれない夢がある
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.50,0:00:38.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そうよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.10,0:00:44.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}創られた世界の中を
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.50,0:00:52.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}抜け出して　自由になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.50,0:00:59.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}走り続けて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.50,0:01:05.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}空に屆けば
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.50,0:01:11.00,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}風になれると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.50,0:01:17.00,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そう信じてるから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.50,0:01:23.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I never give up forever
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.90,0:01:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好燙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.80,0:02:13.80,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}茶色瞳孔中映出的景象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.31,0:02:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問 是你駕駛這個的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.92,0:02:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個不是你駕駛的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.73,0:02:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被幹掉了是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.23,0:02:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那手槍是真的吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.73,0:02:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以借我摸摸嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.64,0:02:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想也知道不行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.84,0:02:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一下子而已嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.34,0:02:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.08,0:03:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來到這鬼地方 沒想到還會遇到小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.49,0:03:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你一臉天下太平的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.69,0:03:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個衛星殖民地應該有軍隊的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.10,0:03:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這還是第一次看到戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.60,0:03:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正的機動戰土也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.50,0:03:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉姆型機動戰士也是第一次看到？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.31,0:03:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼等也不會讓你碰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.32,0:03:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.83,0:03:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯讓我摸摸嗎？太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.57,0:04:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍到了什麼呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.88,0:04:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼！？是我也！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.08,0:04:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.58,0:04:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真會拍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.39,0:04:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的也！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.59,0:04:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.89,0:04:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你姐姐嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.29,0:04:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還給我 快還給我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.29,0:04:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不像是一般的貨櫃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.20,0:04:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還給我 還給我 還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.70,0:04:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 等一下啦 不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.51,0:04:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.51,0:04:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.20,0:04:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.90,0:04:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.90,0:04:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.27,0:05:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.47,0:05:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用那個和我換如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.07,0:05:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.18,0:05:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是騙人的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.48,0:05:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我答應你啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.70,0:05:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾•佛烈德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.70,0:05:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.91,0:05:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.41,0:05:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得到我想要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.42,0:05:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事可是秘密哦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.82,0:05:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.68,0:06:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.68,0:06:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.69,0:06:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到手了 到手了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.69,0:06:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這究竟是怎麼一回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.69,0:06:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是慘不忍睹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.69,0:06:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來幫一下忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.90,0:06:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.69,0:06:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.69,0:07:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行嗎？馬上就來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.69,0:07:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請讓一下 快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.69,0:07:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為事出突然 躲都來不及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.66,0:07:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.97,0:07:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這種時候 你在這兒做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.47,0:07:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點事啦！老師是否發脾氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.37,0:07:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為上午停課所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.07,0:07:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸運啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.58,0:07:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.58,0:07:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的看到了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.49,0:07:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快看那女的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.76,0:07:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還說聯邦沒有機動戰士嗎？白癡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.60,0:07:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天放假不用上課了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.20,0:08:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好極了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.66,0:08:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾•佛烈德伍長 即刻出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.49,0:08:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錯不了 是自北極發射的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.46,0:08:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這錄影磁片怎麼來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.30,0:09:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在返回Side6途中與聯邦軍交戰時 我軍戰士得手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.34,0:09:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是你們的北極危難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.14,0:09:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被月球上所解救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.34,0:09:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得那是中校判斷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.55,0:09:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說那基地是個研究設施的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.95,0:09:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說若照你的提議便沒事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.86,0:09:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次作戰之所以失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.86,0:09:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那幫傢伙也笨得像石頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.86,0:09:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦的手段也並不怎麼高明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.26,0:09:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太空梭也偽裝 太小題大做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.77,0:09:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是不願交予我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.27,0:09:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.58,0:09:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了奪回戰事 付出那麼多的犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.98,0:09:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還想搶回那個？只能把它毀掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.58,0:09:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新人類用的機動戰士嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.59,0:09:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次的作戰也請你多發表意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.89,0:09:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要50個士兵的事我認可了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.89,0:10:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如你所願已選好了優秀的駕駛員 期待你的表現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.40,0:10:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.10,0:10:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正只是一時意氣用事 被打下一架渣古而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.50,0:10:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要有心理準備啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.61,0:10:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.01,0:10:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這叫因禍得福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.71,0:10:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去當炮灰吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.21,0:10:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.21,0:10:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要一幅要揍人的面孔 給人的印象可不好呦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.31,0:10:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你給我這麼多關照！！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.62,0:10:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,15點30分！正好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.62,0:10:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴納德•懷茲曼伍長報到！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.83,0:10:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.65,0:10:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 坐吧 懷茲曼伍長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.25,0:10:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.49,0:11:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 那麼我們就開始作戰的說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.69,0:11:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作戰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.40,0:11:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 作戰到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特務部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.41,0:11:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天起你被編入了我們部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.91,0:11:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旁邊的叫米哈爾 對面那個是加西亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.02,0:11:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是隊長 記住了沒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.12,0:11:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有印象了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.02,0:11:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.02,0:11:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說話很含糊的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.12,0:11:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話不清楚是會死哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.63,0:11:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又有了一項任務重大的作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.63,0:11:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在前幾天你攻擊的那個衛星殖民地裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.73,0:11:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的任務是將偽裝成民用貨船的船駛入那個衛星殖民地的港口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.04,0:11:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝的是新型的機動戰土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.64,0:11:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們三個將先潛入衛星殖民地 偽裝成平民來接收貨物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.75,0:12:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只要穿過戰鬥空域 到港口即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.58,0:12:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.59,0:12:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偽裝成民用船可能被自己人開火射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.89,0:12:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這種被自己人的子彈打下來的喪家犬 我的部隊可不需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.80,0:12:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.40,0:12:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.90,0:12:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作戰的行動代號為“路比根計畫”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.91,0:12:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於今日23:00展開 結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.64,0:12:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾•佛烈德•伊茲魯哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.94,0:13:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.08,0:13:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道我為什麼讓你來的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.68,0:13:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次的全校統考的成績真是不堪入目啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.28,0:13:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,數學D 國語C- 化學C-
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.39,0:13:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社會D- 給我往這兒看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若再繼續考這種成績
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.39,0:13:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只好請你家長或監護人來一趟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.60,0:13:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要誰來好呢？監護人 還是媽媽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.60,0:13:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 畢竟是全國統考 果然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.81,0:13:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回來了 回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.51,0:13:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾 你還活著嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.41,0:13:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 被那個歇斯底里的女人訓了些什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.32,0:13:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真服了她了 她嚇唬我說要把考試的情況告訴我父母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.42,0:13:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我爸媽插手管的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.12,0:13:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包准我一個月不能出門玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.23,0:13:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這未免也太嚴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.83,0:13:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！太嚴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.93,0:14:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.17,0:14:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎沒精打采的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.70,0:14:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.10,0:14:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是否被欺負了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.37,0:14:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.48,0:14:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好 考試成績差不多快公佈了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.59,0:14:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.60,0:15:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逮住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.77,0:15:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.27,0:15:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚了在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.08,0:15:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友在玩“試膽”遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.88,0:15:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不會告訴我媽的吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.48,0:15:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秘密行動是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.38,0:15:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.79,0:15:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我保證啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.89,0:15:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次帶我一起去好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.66,0:15:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.30,0:15:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事可是秘密哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.90,0:15:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,規定女人不能參加的 再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.90,0:15:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人不行呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.87,0:16:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來 武器好像被回收了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.39,0:16:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.90,0:16:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.46,0:17:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那邊很窄 小心點！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.47,0:17:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.67,0:17:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屍體！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.77,0:17:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.38,0:17:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彼此都不要跟著對方好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.09,0:17:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.79,0:17:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特務艦 出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.89,0:17:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.51,0:18:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離作戰開始還有20分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.84,0:18:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“米諾夫斯基粒子”3分鐘後開始散佈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.84,0:18:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎 特務艦先出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.35,0:18:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特務艦向Side6出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.45,0:18:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.37,0:18:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作戰前5分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.28,0:18:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士隊出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.08,0:18:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士隊出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.79,0:18:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.66,0:18:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.44,0:19:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要衝了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油呀！爛機器！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.38,0:19:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是貨船“紅鈴號” 聽到的話 請讓我入港
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.99,0:19:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是貨船“紅鈴號” 聽到的話 請讓我入港
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.19,0:19:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是貨船“紅鈴號” 請回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.39,0:19:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到的話 請讓我入港
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.40,0:20:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.12,0:20:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是戰鬥 在衛星殖民地的外面正在開戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.95,0:21:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真傷腦筋 外面好慘烈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.59,0:21:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同伴被幹掉了 能不能幫我抬他下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.00,0:21:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,護照及入港許可證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.10,0:21:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪亞的政府也該更靠得住些才行 否則我們也很為難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.20,0:21:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟在我的上方“砰”的一聲 一部機動戰士被趕掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.51,0:21:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我怎麼做生意呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.71,0:21:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說出姓名和登錄編號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.41,0:21:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴爾塔•佩塔澤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.31,0:21:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身份證號碼PG40983726
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.02,0:21:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,運載物品的內容說明與發貨單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.62,0:21:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 手腳要更輕些 又不是布偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.73,0:21:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簽收用的保證書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.93,0:21:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,證件就只有這些了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.93,0:21:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若沒證件 就得做檢查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.04,0:21:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.14,0:21:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是否裝了什麼見不得人的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.74,0:21:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事 何必…何必為了張小小的證件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.94,0:22:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也並非閒耗 去把證件辦齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.58,0:22:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是B423甲板 即刻檢查貨物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.29,0:22:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於趕上了 快點搬下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.19,0:22:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手 還沒檢查過 不准動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.86,0:22:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 我是收貨的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.30,0:22:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這便是保證書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.70,0:22:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手續是齊全了 但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.60,0:22:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這本應由運輸船提出的特殊證件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.41,0:22:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是本公司爭取到的工作機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.21,0:22:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若不準時交貨 得負擔損失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.22,0:22:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來本公司將破產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.02,0:22:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,且對對方也不好交代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.52,0:22:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託一下嘛！已沒時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.03,0:22:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 好 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.89,0:22:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？真太感激你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.83,0:22:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也因戰爭而受到上面的壓力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.83,0:22:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次千萬得將證件備齊啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.74,0:23:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡過頭了 被媽媽發現就不妙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.39,0:23:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.29,0:23:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 找死啊 小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.89,0:24:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了 吉翁軍來這個衛星殖民地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.99,0:24:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:15.20,0:25:21.31,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}噓をついた夜には
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:21.51,0:25:27.31,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眠れずに　怖かった
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:28.00,0:25:33.70,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どんな喧嘩をしても
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:34.30,0:25:41.00,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}次の日は　忘れていた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:43.10,0:25:48.50,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}空が　青いこと
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:48.40,0:25:54.91,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}それが　嬉しくて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:55.70,0:26:02.00,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか人を疑い
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:02.70,0:26:08.31,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生きる寂しさ知る事も
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:08.90,0:26:14.31,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}気がつかずに全てを
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:15.60,0:26:20.31,SongJap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}信じてた頃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:47.50,0:26:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我答應你 不會告訴任何人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:52.50,0:26:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是當真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:54.50,0:26:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並不是拿著搶和別人戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:12.10,0:27:15.79,NTitle,,0000,0000,0000,,彩虹的盡頭有什麼？
